data.title: Log Books & Safety Cages
data.text:
As of 1 January 2020, CAMS will be known as Motorsport Australia. Despite this rebrand, your existing CAMS log book remains current and valid and you do not need to do anything.

You can request a new Motorsport Australia log book by contacting the Membership Hotline on 1300 883 959.
